task.summary: Implemented pub-sub , event send and receive callbacks
Added acknowledgement on server side as well as implemented subscribe failure and publish failure acks
Added reconnection facility to the API ( Need to add subscribed channels again )
Added channel facility and subscription to channels on reconnection
Added code for removing channel when unsubscribed the same
Created package and respective jar file for dependency management
Setting reconnect to null after disconnect
Logging system is set up instead of sout
Updated artifact , added code to remove channel when unsubscribed
Optimized the code and updated user friendly callbacks
Removed simple.Json and added Org.Json and added some useful methods
Made some methods private and added methods for removing callbacks
cleanup of idea files, gradle generated files and class files
